The application shall include:
a description of the applicant's professional qualifications, including medical education information and, if appropriate, board certifications and licensure status;
the utilization management procedures and policies to be used by the health maintenance organization; and
certification by the medical director that the utilization management procedures and policies are:
objective;
clinically valid;
compatible with established principles of health care; and
flexible enough to allow deviations from the norms when justified on a case by case basis.
